signal(set,character,S)
What is your name, prodigious new arrival?
---
signal(set,character,you)
...
--- 
...Rosa...
---
...are you... the devil?
---
signal(set,character,S)
An angel that deserted actually, a mistake humans seem to repeat more and more frequently.
---
signal(set,character,you)
So... shouldn't you be punishing us?
---
signal(set,character,S)
Another mistake of your contemporaries it seems. I have been thrown as the first commiter of the worst of sins, my body displayed for all to know what awaits those who believe themselves to be have a judgement above god.
---
signal(set,character,you)
Wouldn't make much sense for you to punish us, I see.
---
signal(set,character,S)
Heh, dare i say is my punishment to have you here, seeing how far humanity has come, and yet end impeded and broken by the cold where no light shines.
name: start
